Interface ObjName

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObjNameBall, ObjNameFlagBottom, ObjNameFlagCenter, ObjNameFlagCornerLeft, ObjNameFlagCornerRight, ObjNameFlagGoalEast, ObjNameFlagGoalLeft, ObjNameFlagGoalRight, ObjNameFlagGoalWest, ObjNameFlagLeft, ObjNameFlagPenaltyEast, ObjNameFlagPenaltyWest, ObjNameFlagRight, ObjNameFlagTop, ObjNameLine, ObjNameNull, ObjNamePlayerEast, ObjNamePlayerWest

    public interface ObjName
    The interface for all objects on the pitch. This is used to translate them so that they are relative to each team (ie. ourGoal, theirGoal)
    Author:
    Atan
